Dr Iqbal Survé sat down with Alec Hogg of BizNews where they discussed his journey of media ownership, entrepreneurship, reputational risk and technology investment.  Survé is the chairman of Sekunjalo Investments and the non executive chairman of Independent Media.  During the interview,  Survé says that Independent Media makes up 3% of his group's assets.  Watch the full interview below:  BUSINESS REPORT